<HEADLINE>
<P>
PAT HARVEY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 We were pleased that LaVera Porter Williams recognized Pat Harvey as an 
important local anchor (letter, Aug. 4) However, we must point out that Harvey 
can be seen weekdays on KCAL TV Channel 9, not Channel 5. 
</P>
<P>
 Harvey has been an integral part of KCAL's award-winning "Prime 9 News" 
efforts since the program's inception in March, 1990. The co-anchor of the 
station's 7 p.m. and 9 p.m. newscasts, Harvey was recently honored with Emmys 
for her "Sex & Aids in Russia" series, both for program content and for her 
excellence as the host. 
</P>
<P>
 SUZANNE LOWE 
</P>
<P>
 KCAL PR Manager 
</P>
