lobster-gathering at the plant as widespread. 
</P>
<P>
 He was charged with illegal possession of short lobsters, taking lobsters by 
illegal means and without a license and possessing an egg-bearing female 
lobster. If convicted, he faces up to a year in jail and a $30,000 fine. 
