 Art: Bucking the analog-to-digital trend, MCA/Universal Animation Art plans to 
release bronze sculpture versions of Jurassic Park's computer-generated 
dinosaurs this fall. Limited-edition serigraphs and lithographs of 
Tyrannosaurus rex and the velociraptors will also be marketed in conjunction 
with the October video release of the film. AMY HARMON 
