 A spokesman for Cisco said the company expects Newport Systems to increase in 
size and does not anticipate any layoffs at the company, which now employs 55 
people. Newport Systems, which recently moved to Irvine from Newport Beach, 
will continue operating under its own name, the Cisco spokesman said. 
