<P>
Profile 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA080994-0263 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 068420 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
August 9, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 2; Column 2; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
